{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act11d0_level_act11d0_03_beg","storyGroup":"act11d0","storySort":6,"storyDependence":"act11d0_level_act11d0_02_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"TW-3","storyName":"高塔烟火","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"没想到的是，医疗点不久前被人烧毁，种种表现意味着安托凶多吉少。失落的亚叶想要回去确认安托的遗体，却在这时遭遇了正在进攻城市的泥岩小队的感染者。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act11d0/level_act11d0_03_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act11d0_03","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":4,"next":6,"characters":["铃兰","亚叶","塔佳娜","武装的感染者"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"九尾狐活动 3上","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_bg_bg_ltruins.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":7},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"这......这是......","id":8,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......","id":10,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":11},{"type":"character","id":12},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":13},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#3","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"是罗德岛的物资箱没错，有编号，有日期。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......是上一次定期联络的时候，是我亲自......","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"亚叶姐姐......","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#3","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"火灾是怎么发生的？","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"事故——本来是这样定性的，但是......","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"但是这里有明显的施术痕迹，安托医生是个很认真的人，当然不会留下太危险的易燃物。","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"我们确认不了明显的起火点，帐篷的金属支架都被融化了，而且尸体......","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"啊......","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......没事的，继续吧。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"根据遗体情况判断，受害者们几乎没能离开帐篷，更不存在挣扎，一瞬间就面目全非。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"我不认为普通的火灾能让安托医生和患者们这么简单就被......","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"除非，是源石技艺，而且不像是普通的火焰，是依赖某种手段达成的瞬间高温......","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"——这之中有几个感染者？","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"欸？啊......镇上的感染者有三人，凯文、毕德曼、埃克哈德，他们在这里接受治疗，以及......","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"以及......托尔，托尔瓦尔德。","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"他是长官的独子，是我的老朋友......他不是感染者，他只是去帮忙的，出于好心。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"......塔佳娜小姐，如果你感到难过的话，说出来比较好喔。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_069#4","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"欸？","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8c/Avg_avg_npc_069_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_069#4","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我能感觉到，这里充斥着悲伤。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"这里......这里有很多不甘心，很多快乐，很多痛苦，但是现在都不存在了。","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_069#2","focus":"2","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"这是......也是某种源石技艺吗？","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_069#2","focus":"1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"不——只是看多了这样的事情，大家都喜欢把自己的想法藏起来，但这样不好喔。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"可能只是我多想了，不过，如果总是勉强自己的话，会让身边的人担心吧？","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"可以哭一场的，不会有人说什么的啦。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_069","focus":"2","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"嗯，谢谢，其实我也清楚，但是现在我还不能......不能松懈。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_069_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_069","focus":"1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嗯——","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......别、别看着我，我知道啦，丽萨你就不用担心了。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嗯！","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_char_358_lisa_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"唉......那什么，抱歉！","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"欸？怎么突然......？","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8c/Avg_avg_npc_069_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......我在离开罗德岛本舰的时候已经做好心理准备了，安托她是个很认真的人，所以她向来守时。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我怎么会真的不清楚干员失联意味着什么，罗德岛经历过多少次这样的生死离别，我只是不愿意相信罢了。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"呼......就是，那个，刚才太激动了，我很抱歉。","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"这场谋杀之中遭受损失的，不止是罗德岛。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"......八具遗体都被塞弗林长官带走了。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"因为镇上没有感染者处理专家，所以我们只能草草埋葬他们......","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"他们不能跟着沃伦姆德一起前进，他们会被埋葬在城镇之外的废土上，等沃伦姆德离开这里，他们就永远失去了家乡。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"本来......按照我们的传统......至少可以不用这样的......","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_358_lisa_1#3","focus":"2","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"这种事情......很常见。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_char_358_lisa_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"八具遗体？","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"八具遗体，除了刚才说的五个人，此外的应该是来这里接受治疗的游荡者......","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"大裂谷崩裂时，沃伦姆德并没能全身而退，当然也有很多周边的商人、旅行者被卷入了天灾。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"尽管在那之后，沃伦姆德的处境越发糟糕，但除了追逐着这座仍旧勉强前进在废土上的城镇之外，他们也没有别的办法。","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"这期间，难民们的队伍也在变化......不过安托医生一视同仁，她也会负责救助一些愿意被救助的感染者。","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"所以，一位非感染者，七位感染者......","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"感染者的遗体呢？在生命体征停止的数分钟到数小时内，视体内源石融合率，可能会出现二次扩散，如果不进行专门处理的话很危险。","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"啊，那个，塞弗林长官判断因为感染程度较轻，而且高温迅速摧毁了身体组织，所以不存在太大风险......","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......不是说没有专业人士吗？","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"诶，塞弗林长官说自己只是按照经验判断，他也没十足的把握......","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"经验......什么样的工作才会有处理感染者尸体的经验......","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"不过，也是，如果失去了亲生骨肉还能保持冷静，也许他并没有表面上那么轻浮。","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我想回去检查一下各位感染者的遗体......我想见安托一眼。","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"当然可以，我会向长官解释的，不过大部分遗体炭化严重，我们分辨不出来.......","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_069_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"没关系——","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"啊——！","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_char_358_lisa_4.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":105},{"type":"character","id":106},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_ac11_3.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"0.9","yScale":"0.9","id":108},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"丽萨？","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"这个牌子......","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"啊......安托的工作牌，竟然没有烧毁......","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......对了。","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"她工作的时候，总是会抱怨工作牌碍事。很奇怪吧？明明大家都会挂在胸前，也不知道哪里碍事了......","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我们走吧，我想见她......我想见见她。","id":115},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":116},{"type":"dialog","id":117},{"type":"character","id":118},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":119},{"type":"image","id":120},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":121},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"2","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":122},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","volume":"0.1","id":123},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":124},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#3","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"轰鸣——？","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$frontline_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_frontline_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":127,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"方向——是城镇的方向！","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8c/Avg_avg_npc_069_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"亚、亚叶姐姐！好像有什么人在靠近！","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_char_358_lisa_4.png"},{"type":"character","id":132},{"type":"dialog","id":133},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":134},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"......嗯？","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"啊，那个标志......是罗德岛......？你们什么时候......","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#3","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"这个装扮......可不像是普通的感染者啊。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"是莱塔尼亚人？还是之前提到过的萨卡兹？","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#3","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"......他们是最近出现在城镇周围的感染者武装分子，由一批来路不明的萨卡兹为主心骨，之后接纳了许多本地的感染者......","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/55/Avg_avg_npc_069_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"他们自称——“泥岩小队”。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/55/Avg_avg_npc_069_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":145},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":146},{"type":"character","id":147},{"type":"image","id":148}],"characters":["铃兰","亚叶","塔佳娜","武装的感染者"]}